data.description: Pack your bags and be ready to move right in! It is located in the much sought-after Oliver Crossing in Leeds but in St. Clair County, where the property taxes are SO much lower. Open concept living room/dining/kitchen with cathedral ceilings in the living room; wood burning fireplace (previously set up for propane gas logs); large main bedroom w/ensuite & large walk-in closet; 2 additional bedrooms & a full bath. Beautifully updated kitchen with freshly painted cabinets a new look!  The back patio is covered & screened & is an excellent location for morning coffee. Nice, low, maintenance vinyl privacy fence around the back yard. 2 car garage with added concrete pad for additional parking. Come Home to Oliver Crossing!!!!!!!!!!!
